reviews.text:
The food quality is acceptable but the attitude of the waiters could still be improved.
Also the price is a bit expensive.
Quite good. The one dollars for one chicken is cheap and delicious.

The food presentation was nice but was very oily (much more oily than other restaurants) and the service was very poor. The servers looked really tire. We were there around 2:30pm. The environment was very noisy and it did not help when the servers were throwing dirty plates, cups and utensils really hard into collection bins. The clanking noise was driving me crazy and there was no way to chat with friends. In addition, the cashiers were not polite.
Average but not bad, too many maiNland

I eat at night and the foods are very bad and not fresh , most of products are alreday cooked and packed from China. Even the price is fair but the quality of foods need to improve. I taste a little and stop eating anymore.

result.name: Amoy Plaza

reviews.text: Old private estate shopping mall struggling to compete with new ones.  It is not the new huge malls with high ceilings big brands but you may like the surprises and the rare shops at the corners or far end of corridors.  There are a few shops selling expert model kits for adults and toys for teenagers and game console games also.
Many good restaurants, many hobby stores. Something for everyone. Best of all, affordable price.
Many delicious food such as Genki Sushi and Pizza Hut

A lot of choices to choose from, a cinema and stuff like that. What you would hope from a decent shopping mall. There are also housing estates above the shopping centre but ofc it's too expensive for a normal human being in Hong Kong to afford
Nice concentrated shops and diversity.

reviews.text: 服務態度極差👎
說什麼都好吃，那是騙人的，不過幾款菜式還是可以的。

下午茶優惠時間，餐具真係幾污糟! 咁衰遇到啲帶位姐姐同擺位阿姐都唔係無用心做野，拎啲餐具嚟仲黏住的食物碎，有水又有油漬！係啲上餐姐姐服務語氣正常啲。。。。蜜汁排骨真係舖住成堆骨，好咸！
其他食物味道還可以。
